---
// 字体决策的最后残页: 只剩"Lexend 做正文"的长文样张(印说想最后看一眼).
// 站上正式字体已定 V2 三件套(Source Serif Pro / Noto Sans / Fira Code, 见 tokens.css).
// 印看完说一声 → 整页删除 + 卸载 lexend 包.
import '@fontsource-variable/lexend/index.css';
import BaseLayout from '../../components/layout/BaseLayout.astro';
import { about } from '../../lib/data';
---

<BaseLayout title="Type lab — Ender Jones" description="Lexend body sample, last look." noindex>
  <main style="--ej-page-w: 760px;">
    <section class="reveal" style="--reveal-i: 0;">
      <p class="ej-kicker">TYPE LAB — LAST LOOK · LEXEND AS BODY</p>
      <h1 class="ej-h1 ej-h1--sm">Lexend 长文样张.<span class="ej-caret" aria-hidden="true"></span></h1>
      <p class="ej-sub">
        全站已换 V2 三件套; 这页只回答一个问题 — "正文 Lexend 是不是 over 了".
        下面同一篇文字, 上半 Lexend, 下半 Noto Sans(现役), 都在文章字号(18.5px)排到阅读长度. 看完说一声, 这页就删.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="lab reveal" style="--reveal-i: 1;">
      <article class="ej-card block" style="--ej-sans: 'Lexend Variable', system-ui, sans-serif;">
        <p class="tag">LEXEND</p>
        <div class="sample">
          {about.paras.map((p) => (
            <p>{p}</p>
          ))}
          <p>
            The worklog exists because my working memory can't be trusted with a whole day. One line at capture,
            a small ritual at close, git as the spine: done beats todo, dropping a task is a decision rather than
            a failure, and blank days count against nothing. Lexend was drawn to reduce visual crowding — wide
            apertures, generous spacing — which is exactly why long paragraphs of it can feel airy to the point
            of loose: the words stop holding hands.
          </p>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="ej-card block">
        <p class="tag">NOTO SANS(现役)</p>
        <div class="sample">
          {about.paras.map((p) => (
            <p>{p}</p>
          ))}
          <p>
            The worklog exists because my working memory can't be trusted with a whole day. One line at capture,
            a small ritual at close, git as the spine: done beats todo, dropping a task is a decision rather than
            a failure, and blank days count against nothing. Noto Sans keeps a quieter rhythm — narrower, denser,
            closer to what decades of print taught your eyes to expect from a paragraph.
          </p>
        </div>
      </article>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .lab {
    display: grid;
    gap: 14px;
    padding: clamp(28px, 4vh, 40px) 0 clamp(56px, 8vh, 72px);
  }
  .block {
    padding: 22px 26px 24px;
  }
  .tag {
    margin: 0 0 14px;
    color: var(--ej-pink-2);
    font-family: var(--ej-mono);
    font-size: var(--ej-fs-micro);
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
  }
  .sample {
    display: grid;
    gap: 14px;
  }
  .sample p {
    margin: 0;
    max-width: 62ch;
    color: #b8b8c0;
    font-family: var(--ej-sans);
    font-size: var(--ej-fs-lede);
    line-height: 1.75;
    text-wrap: pretty;
  }
</style>
